作者 | 江山编辑 | 张国2月5日，中国青年报·中国青年网记者看到的一份湖北省广水市二医院紧缺物资需求清单显示，该院医用防护面罩、医用护目镜、防护鞋套等许多物品的库存数量都是“0”。
A list of shortages seen by China Youth Daily's China Youth Daily yesterday showed that many items in the hospital's medical protection mask, medical goggles, and protective shoes were in stock at the No. 2 Hospital in Hubei province.
广水市是随州市下辖的县级市之一。
Guangzhou is one of the county-level cities under the jurisdiction of Suizhou.
广水市二医院后勤物资保障负责人向记者确认，这是广水新冠肺炎疫情防控两家定点医院之一，需求清单里的情况是真实的。
Guangzhou Second Hospital logistics supplies to the reporter confirmed that this is Guangshui New Crown Pneumonia prevention and control of one of the two designated hospitals, the list of needs is true.
“我们只能把用过的护目镜、面罩消毒重复使用，鞋套自己找人加工。
"We can only use the goggles, face mask disinfection reuse, shoe cover for their own processing.
一次性手部消毒液到处买不到，只能用酒精自制。
Disposable hand sanitizers are not available everywhere, but can only be made with alcohol.
”他告诉记者，广水二医院共有100多名医护人员，医用物资“都是东拼西凑”，没有N95口罩等急用的必需品。
He told reporters that there were more than 100 medical staff at Guangshui II Hospital, and the medical supplies were "patchwork" and there were no emergency necessities such as N95 masks.
图自网络连日来，来自湖北省随州市的医院求助信息在社交平台传播。
From the network for days, from Suizhou City, Hubei Province, hospital help information spread on social platforms.
2月5日下午，中国青年报·中国青年网记者从随州市新冠肺炎疫情防控指挥部和随州市中心医院等渠道了解到，目前随州已收到部分捐赠，但因为物流原因，医用防护物资仍处于紧缺状态。
February 5 afternoon, China Youth Daily China Youth Net reporters from the Suizhou New Crown Pneumonia Prevention and Control Command and Suizhou Central Hospital and other sources learned that the state has received some donations, but the medical protection materials are still in short supply for logistical reasons.
截至2月4日24时，湖北省累计报告新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎病例16678例，其中随州706例。
As of 2400 hours February 4, a total of 16,678 new cases of coronavirus infection were reported in Hubei Province, including 706 cases in Suizhou Province.
随州市的常住人口为220多万，与其他城市相比，确诊病例占比处于高位。
With a resident population of more than 2.2 million, Suizhou has a high proportion of confirmed cases compared with other cities.
2月3日，随州市唯一的三甲医院——随州市中心医院发布接受社会捐赠的公告，列出的紧缺防护物资耗材清单有“医用外科口罩、N95口罩、一次性医用口罩、医用防护服、隔离衣、一次性手术衣、防护面罩、防冲击眼罩、医用鞋套等”。
On February 3, Suizhou Central Hospital, the only Sanjia hospital in Suizhou City, issued a notice accepting social donations. The list of consumables included "medical surgical masks, N95 masks, disposable medical masks, medical masks, medical protective clothing, disposable surgical clothes, protective masks, impact masks, medical shoe covers, etc."
图自网络随州市疫情防控指挥部工作人员告诉记者，当地已陆续收到社会捐赠的款物。
Picture from the network of epidemic prevention and control command staff told reporters that the local community has been receiving donations of money and goods.
2月4日起，随州市在城区禁行私家车、网约车、出租车，“为了尽量把大家都隔离在家里”。
February 4, Suizhou City in the prohibition of private cars, network cars, taxis, "in order to try to isolate everyone at home."
指挥部另一位参与物资保障工作的工作人员告诉记者，随州市已向湖北省委、省政府报告，2月5日，湖北省委副书记、省长王晓东已到随州协调解决问题。
Another member of the headquarters staff involved in material security told reporters that Suizhou had reported to the Hubei Provincial Committee and the provincial government that on February 5, the vice-secretary of the Hubei Provincial Committee, Governor Wang Xiaodong, had arrived in Suizhou to coordinate and solve the problem.
在网上发布的众多求助信息中，其中一则称，“随州的经济发展水平在全省比较落后，医疗资源匮乏，只有随州市中心医院一家三甲医院。
"The level of economic development across the province is backward and medical resources are scarce," said one of the many help messages posted online.
随州仅有内蒙古一支4人医疗队增援……急需医疗队、物资支援和政策帮扶。
Suizhou only Inner Mongolia a 4-member medical team to reinforce...... urgent need of medical teams, material support and policy assistance.
”随州市疫情防控指挥部工作人员介绍，截至2月5日，当地确实只有一支来自内蒙古的4人医疗队前来支援。
As of February 5, only a four-member medical team from Inner Mongolia had arrived to support the epidemic in Suizhou, officials said.
这支医疗队于1月31日到达随州。
The medical team arrived in Suizhou on 31 January.
随州市前几日感染者数量迅速增加，一个原因是外来专家来了比较先进的仪器，检测出了许多疑似患者，目前新增确诊病例人数已在逐渐下降，2月4日新增65例确诊病例，较前一天新增的183例已有下降。
One of the reasons for the rapid increase in the number of infected people in Suizhou in the past few days is that the number of newly confirmed cases has gradually decreased, with the number of confirmed cases falling from 183 the previous day to 65 on February 4.
随州市中心医院办公室一名工作人员告诉记者，目前该院最短缺的是防护服、口罩和护目镜，特别是防护服。
Suizhou central hospital office staff told reporters that the hospital is the most shortage of protective clothing, masks and goggles, especially protective clothing.
为了节约防护服，医生和护士连续上一天班而不更换，只能穿成人纸尿裤以解决内急。
To save on protective clothing, doctors and nurses work all day long without replacing them. Instead, they wear adult diapers to deal with emergencies.
她介绍，求助信息发布后，该院陆续收到一些捐赠物资，物资紧缺状况得到一定缓解，但其中许多不符合医疗标准，“有很多（口罩）都是一次性的，他们（医护人员）都用不了”。
She said the hospital had received donations since the release of the information and the shortages had eased somewhat, but many of them did not meet medical standards. "A lot of [masks] are disposable and they can't be used."
她告诉记者， 随州市中心医院“把所有的医护人员全部都调动起来了，从大年三十起就没休息，许多后勤人员也去一线了”。
She told reporters that the central hospital in Suizhou "all the medical personnel are mobilized, from about 30 did not rest, many logisticians also went to the line.
在物资供应上，一个实际困难是物流不畅。
One of the practical difficulties in the supply of materials is poor logistics.
随州市中心医院这位工作人员告诉记者，前几日只有顺丰和中国邮政两家物流公司提供服务，近两日顺丰也停运了。
Suizhou central hospital staff told reporters, the last few days only Shunfeng and China Post logistics companies to provide services, nearly two days Shunfeng also stopped.
该院负责后勤物资的另一位工作人员介绍：“我们也在努力地给供货厂商做工作，因为有好多物资从运输上面有困难，沟通好了他不一定能进来”。
"We are also working hard to work with suppliers because there are so many things out there that it's difficult for him to get in," said another of the hospital's logistics staff.
顺丰速运客服表示，目前寄往随州的快件限重3公斤，因陆路交通已停运，只能走航运。
According to the company, the current express shipment to Suizhou is limited to 3kg because overland traffic has been suspended and can only be transported by sea.
此外，有在随州市基层医院联系物资采购的知情人士介绍，随州下辖县级市的医护人员和医疗物资也面临缺口，除了口罩、防护服、护目镜这类物资，在疫情防控工作中常用的红外体温检测仪也不足。
In addition, people familiar with the procurement of materials at the basic level hospitals in Suizhou City have said that medical personnel and medical supplies under the jurisdiction of the county level in Suizhou are facing a shortage of materials such as masks, protective clothing, goggles and other commonly used infrared thermometers in disease control work.
据湖北当地媒体报道，2月5日，湖北省委副书记、省长王晓东在随州市、孝感市检查指导疫情防控工作。
Hubei province on February 5, deputy secretary and governor Wang Xiaodong in Suizhou City, Xiaoyan City, to guide the epidemic prevention and control work, local media reported.
针对基层反映的医疗技术力量不足、医疗物资缺口较大等问题，王晓东现场调度有关部门立即解决，并叮嘱要科学合理调配使用，确保把有限资源用在刀刃上，努力提高收治率和治愈率、降低感染率和病死率。
In view of the shortage of medical technology and the shortage of medical materials at the grass-roots level, Wang Xiaodong dispatched the relevant departments to solve the problem immediately, and instructed them to allocate and use them scientifically and rationally to ensure that the limited resources were spent on knives and to improve the acceptance and cure rates and reduce the infection and death rates.
（本文由中国青年报独立出品，首发在中国青年报客户端及头条号，加入树木计划。
(This article is produced independently by China Youth Daily. It is first published in China Youth Daily client and headline number.
